<pre><code>2、修改文章类型categories[通过vim编辑]
</code></pre><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ vim source/_posts/new-Types.md </div><div class="line">   ---</div><div class="line">   title: new Types</div><div class="line">   date: 2016-08-25 20:23:37</div><div class="line">   categories: type1</div><div class="line">   description: 这里是内容简介</div><div class="line">   --- </div><div class="line">   我的分类是type1</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
